<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tiān fù wǒ yǒu yī gè hěn shēn de qī dài 迦南895</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tiān fù wǒ yǒu yī gè hěn shēn de qī dài, jiù xiàng hǎi zhōng de bō làng zài wǒ de xīn zhōng péng pài.
 yuàn nǐ quán de de ér nǚ dōu yī tóng xiàng nǐ qǐ lì. shǒu lā shǒu duì nǐ shuō, bà bà wǒ men dōu yào huí lái.
 dōu céng jīng cāng hǎi céng jīng cāng hǎi de cóng róng. dōu céng jīng lù tú céng jīng lù tú shàng de shī bài.
 jīn tiān wǒ men dōu míng bái, měi zuò gū chéng yào lián qǐ lái. cái néng zhù fú quán de, cái huì yǒu nǐ de tóng zài.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>895</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>